content:
The AI Conference 2025 FAQ

These are the most frequently asked questions about The AI Conference 2025. If you don't see an answer you’re looking for, email us at info@aiconference.com and we’ll be happy to assist you!
overview: Introduction to the FAQ section for The AI Conference 2025, including contact information for further inquiries.

content:
General Event Info

Can I attend this event virtually? This is an in-person event only. We promote community and networking and hope to see you there.

Where is this event located? This is an in-person event at Pier 48, Mission Rock, San Francisco, CA 94158.

When is the event? The AI Conference takes place on SEPTEMBER 17th – 18th, 2025 beginning at 8:00 AM PST.
overview: Details about the event format, location, and schedule for The AI Conference 2025.

content:
How can my company sponsor The AI Conference? Please visit: aiconference.com/sponsors/ for all exhibitor opportunities.

Where can I park My Car? The most up to date parking info can be found at Park Wiz.
overview: Information on sponsorship opportunities and parking details for attendees.

content:
The AI Conference 2025 Cost to Attend

How much does The AI Conference 2025 cost? The conference has Early Bird pricing while supplies last. For those who miss our early pricing, the current price of the standard passes can be found on the registration page after launch.
overview: Cost details for attending The AI Conference 2025, including early bird pricing information.

content: Under what circumstances do you offer discounts? Group rates are available to groups of three or more attendees registering together. Contact tickets@aiconference.com to receive a group rate discount code.
overview: Information on group discounts available for attendees registering together.

content: What is the Cancellation policy? The AI Conference offers refunds up to 30 days prior to an event. A fee of 5% will be charged for all refunds. Email tickets@aiconference.com for refund requests.
overview: Cancellation policy for The AI Conference 2025, including refund details.

content: Is there a code of conduct? Please view our code of conduct at aiconference.com/code-of-conduct/
overview: Reference to the code of conduct for attendees at The AI Conference 2025.

content:
Registration for The AI Conference 2025

I have a press, vendor, or speaker pass. What now? The AI Conference will be sending a series of emails that include everything needed to navigate the event including information about meals, transportation, maps, and tips and tricks to getting the most out of your experience.
overview: Guidance for press, vendors, or speakers regarding registration and event navigation.

content: Can I present at the conference? We will open submissions for this year’s conference speakers soon. Be sure to sign up for our speakers interest list to be notified.
overview: Information on the opportunity to present at The AI Conference 2025 and how to sign up for notifications.

content: How do I get a press pass? If you are a member of the press, you can apply for a media pass shortly.
overview: Details on how members of the press can apply for a media pass for the conference.

content:
Presentation information

Who will be speaking at the conference? 2 DAYS | 4 TRACKS | 85+ SPEAKERS. Our ever updating list of speakers, presenters, and sponsors can be found at aiconference.com.
overview: Overview of the presentation format and speaker information for The AI Conference 2025.

content: How long will presentations be? Presentations will be broken into 3 types: Keynote presentations lasting 40 minutes and featured contributors with a duration of 20 minutes. Vendor and sponsor presentations may vary in time and may be revisited throughout the duration of the conference.
overview: Details on the duration and types of presentations at The AI Conference 2025.

content: What topics will be covered? A wide range of topics will be covered including: AGI development, Foundation Models and Large Language Models, Generative AI, Neural Architectures, AI Infrastructure, AI Use Cases, Ethics and Alignment, Data Management tools for AI, AI Startups & Investment, and more.
overview: Topics that will be discussed at The AI Conference 2025.

content: Are there multiple presentation areas? There are 4 main areas at The AI Conference. Four presentation halls, a vendor and sponsor presentation area, and an atrium area where networking mixers and food & beverages are served.
overview: Information on the layout and presentation areas at The AI Conference 2025.

content: Which hotels are near the event? Luma Hotel San Francisco, 100 Channel St, San Francisco, CA 94158, 0.3 mile / 6 min walk. Booking cut off date: 8/29/2025. LUMA Hotel San Francisco is where modern elegance meets the energy of Mission Bay.
overview: Details on nearby hotels for attendees of The AI Conference 2025, including booking information.

content: Hotel VIA, 138 King St, San Francisco, CA 94107, 0.6 mile / 9 min walk. Booking cut off date: 8/18/2025. Overlooking Oracle Park, this boutique retreat blends sleek sophistication with personalized service.
overview: Information on Hotel VIA, a nearby accommodation option for conference attendees.

content: SoMa House, 121 7th Street, San Francisco, CA 94103, 1.9 miles / 11 min car. Booking cut off date: 7/16/2025. Nestled in the heart of San Francisco’s creative district, this stylish retreat blends modern design with a relaxed vibe.
overview: Details about SoMa House, another hotel option for attendees of The AI Conference 2025.

content: Hotel Fiona, 140 7th Street, San Francisco, CA 94103, 1.9 miles / 11 min car. Booking cut off date: 7/16/2025. Situated near popular attractions like Union Square and the Moscone Convention Center.
